psalm.text:
[[Ps 31,3c]]Be my rock of refuge,
[[Ps 31,3d]]a stronghold to give me safety.
[[Ps 31,4]]You are my rock and my fortress; 
for your name's sake you will lead and guide me.

[[Ps 31,6a]]Into your hands I commend my spirit;
[[Ps 31,6b]]you will redeem me, O LORD, O faithful God.
[[Ps 31,7b]]My trust is in the LORD;
[[Ps 31,8a]]I will rejoice and be glad because of your mercy.

[[Ps 31,17]]Let your face shine upon your servant; 
save me in your kindness.
[[Ps 31,21a]]You hide them in the shelter of your presence
[[Ps 31,21b]]from the plottings of men.
